<h1>Burgers!1!!</h1>

<h2>The following is a list of burgers that I want to eat.</h2>

<ul>
    {{#each burgers}}
        {{#unless devoured}}
            {{> burgers/burger-block}}
        {{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>The following is a list of burgers that I have already eaten.</h2>

<ul>
    {{#each burgers}}
        {{#if devoured}}
            {{> burgers/burger-block}}
        {{/if}}
    {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Add a Burger</h2>
<form class="create-form">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="burger">Burger Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="burger" name="name">
  </div>

  <button type="submit">Add Burger</button>
</form>